description: 25K and 50K Time Trials on the roads surrounding Prettyboy Reservoir in Baltimore County, Maryland
course: Race Starts at the intersection of Rayville Rd and Spooks Hill Road.  The race takes place on a rolling and hilly course on the roads surrounding Prettyboy Revervoir. just outside of Baltimore Maryland.  The start line will be at Spooks Hill Rd & Rayville Rd, Parkton, MD 21120
notes: The rider begins at 9:00 AM.  Racers will be go off at 30 second intervals.  Start times will be sent to racers on Friday morning (i.e. 8/22).
directions:
Use your favorite mapping program or GPS to find. Spooks Hill Rd & Rayville Rd, Parkton, MD 21120.

Take Ext 31 (Middletown Road) Toward Parkton, MD.  Turn left at Molesworth RD.  Then turn right onto Armacost Rd.  Finally turn right onto Spooks Hill Rd which will take you to the start.

Parking is 0.5 mile north on Spooks Hill Road from the intersection where the start line is staged.  It is a private lot, and will be marked very well with signage.

description: Held at the new cyclocross practice park at the South Germantown Recreational Park.

directions: The race is held at the South Germantown Rec Park at 18041 Central Park Circle, Germantown, MD 20841
